== Major Shrines Dedicated to Kamunaobi no Kami and Ōnaobi no Kami == * {{ill|Kego Shrine|ja|警固神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kego Shrine|qq=}} – Fukuoka City, Fukuoka Prefecture * {{ill|Sakurai Shrine (Itoshima)|ja|桜井神社 (糸島市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakurai Shrine (Itoshima)|qq=}} – Itoshima City, Fukuoka Prefecture * Naobi Shrine – Nogata City, Fukuoka Prefecture * {{ill|Hayasuihime Shrine|ja|早吸日女神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hayasuihime Shrine|qq=}} – Ōita City, Ōita Prefecture * {{ill|Saikanda Shrine|ja|西寒多神社|1=Sasamuta Shrine|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saikanda Shrine|13=User:Immanuelle/Sasamuta Shrine|qq=}} – Ōita City, Ōita Prefecture * Dewasanzan Shrine, Sanshin Gōsai-den – Tsuruoka City, Yamagata Prefecture * Gosen Hachiman Shrine – Gosen City, Niigata Prefecture * {{ill|Udo Shrine|ja|鵜戸神宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Udo Shrine|qq=}}, within the grounds of Kyūhashira Shrine – Nichinan City, Miyazaki Prefecture * Isonosaji Shrine – Yazu District, Tottori Prefecture * Ōhara Shrine, within the grounds of Sakurai Shrine – Ōnan Town, Shimane Prefecture * Noma Shrine – Imabari City, Ehime Prefecture * Kambe Shrine – Kōshū City, Yamanashi Prefecture * Ōagata Shrine, within the grounds of Kaijo Shrine – Inuyama City, Aichi Prefecture * {{ill|Ikasuri Shrine|ja|坐摩神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikasuri Shrine|qq=}}, within the grounds of Aiden Shrine – Chūō Ward, Osaka City * Ikuto Shrine – Toyooka City, Hyōgo Prefecture * {{ill|Ayato Kuninaka Shrine|ja|綾戸国中神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ayato Kuninaka Shrine|qq=}} – Kyoto City, Kyoto Prefecture * {{ill|Itsukushima Shrine|ja|厳島神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itsukushima Shrine|qq=}} – Hatsukaichi City, Hiroshima Prefecture * {{ill|Isonokami Jingu|lt=Isonokami Jingu|lt=Isonokami Shrine|ja|石上神宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isonokami Shrine|qq=}}, within the grounds of Shichiza Shrine – Tenri City, Nara Prefecture
